yepet ke putra : gomer, magog, madaai, yavan, toobal, meshok, aur teeras hue.
saree prathvee par aek hee bhasha, aur aek hee bolee thee.
jab terah do sau panch varsha ka hua, tab vah haran desh men mar gaya..
jab tak yahova ne sadom aur amora ko nash n kiya tha, tab tak soar ke marga tak vah tarai yahova kee baattkai, aur misr desh ke saman upaja thee.
par jo kuchh in javanon ne kha liya haai aur unaka bhag jo mere sath gaae the arthata aner, aeshkol, aur mamra maain naheen lauttaunga ve to apana apana bhag rakh len..
aur yahova ke doot ne us se kaha, maain tere vansh ko bahut baddhaunga, yahan tak ki bahutayat ke karan usakee ganna n ho sakegee.
aur jab usake putra ishmaael kee khladee ka khtana hua tab vah terah varsha ka tha.
fir us ne us se yah bhee kaha, kadachita vahan chalees milen. us ne kaha, to maain chalees ke karan bhee aeesa ne karoonga.
bhor ko ibraaheem uttkar us sthan ko gaya, jahan vah yahova ke sammukh khda tha
fir parameshvar ne kaha, jal jeeavit praaanaiyon se bahut hee bhr jaa, aur pakshaee prathvee ke upar akash ken antar men uden.
so sara ko ibraaheem se garbhvatee hokar usake buddhape men usee niyukt samay par jo parameshvar ne us se ttharaya tha aek putra utpann hua.
aur ibraaheem ne bershoba men jha ka aek vraksha lagaya, aur vahan yahova, jo sanatan ishvar haai, us se praarthna kee.
he hamare prabhu, hamaree sun : too to hamare beech men bada pradhaan haai : so hamaree kabraen men se jisako too chahe us men apane murde ko gad ham men se koi tujhe apanee kabra ke lene se n rokega, ki too apane murde ko us men gadne n paae.
tab vah das us se bhentt karane ko dauda, aur kaha, apane ghade me se thoda panee mujhe pila de.
fir maain ne sir jhukakar yahova ko dandvata kiya, aur apane svamee ibraaheem ke parameshvar yahova ko dhany kaha, kyonki us ne mujhe tteek marga se pahunchaya ki maai apane svamee ke putra ke liye usakee bhteejee ko le jaun.
ibraaheem ka putra ishmaael jo sara kee laundee hajira misree se utpann hua tha, usakee yah vanshaavalee haai.
tab abeemelek ne isahak ko bulavakar kaha, vah to nishchay teree patnee haai fir too ne kyonkar usako apanee baahin kaha ? isahak ne uttr diya, maain ne socha tha, ki aeesa n ho ki usake karan meree mratyu ho.
tab aesav aher karane ko maaidan men gaya. jab isahak aesav se yah bat kah raha tha, tab ribaka sun rahee thee.
us ne kaha, kya usaka nam yakoob yatharth naheen rakha gaya ? us ne mujhe do bar adnga mara, mera pahilautte ka adhaikar to us ne le hee liya tha : aur ab dek, us ne mera ashaeervad bhee le liya haai : fir us ne kaha, kya too ne mere liye bhee koi ashaeervad naheen soch rakha haai ?
aur maain apane pita ke ghar men kushal kshom se lautt aun : to yahova mera parameshvar ttharega.
tab yakoob rahel ke pas bhee gaya, aur usakee praeeti lia: se aadhaik usee par hui, aur us ne laban ke sath rahakar sat varsha aur usakee seva kee..
jab rahel ne dekha, ki yakoob ke liye mujh se koi santan naheen hota, tab vah apanee bahin se dah karane lagee : aur yakoob se kaha, mujhe bhee santan de, naheen to mar jaungee.
maain aj teree sab bhed-bakaariyon ke beech hokar nikaloonga, aur jo bhed va bakaree chitteevalee va chitkabaree ho, aur jo bhed kalee ho, aur jo bakaree chitkabaree va chitteevalee ho, unhen maain alag kar rakoonga : aur meree majadooree men ve hee ttharengee.
so yakoob laban aramee ke pas se choree se chala gaya, usako n bataya ki maain bhaga jata hoon.
fir laban ne yakoob se kaha, is ddher ko dekh aur is khmbhe ko bhee dek, jinako maain ne apane aur tere beech men khda kiya haai.
aur us ne yakoob se poochha, tera nam kya haai? us ne kaha yakooba.
aur shakem ka pita hamor nikalakar yakoob se batacheet karane ke liye usake pas gaya.
so yakoob un sab samet, jo usake sang the, kanan desh ke looj nagar ko aya. vah nagar betel bhee kahalata haai.
aesav jo aedom bhee kahalata haai : so seir nam pahadee desh men rahane laga.
fir aesavavanshaiyon ke aadhaipaatiyon ke kulo, aur sthanon ke anusar unake nam ye haain arthata timna adhaipaati, alba adhaipaati, yatet aadhaipaati,
so yoosufa ke bhaiyon ne usako us gadhe men se kheenchake bahar nikala, aur ishmaaeliyon ke hath chandee ke bees ttukadon men bech diya : aur ve yoosufa ko misr men le gaae.
tab yahooda ne kaha, achchha, vah bandhak us ke pas rahane de, naheen to ham log tuchchh gine jaaenge: dek, maain ne bakaree ka yah bachcha bhej diya, par vah tujhe naheen milee.
yahova parameshvar ne jitane banaaile pashu banaae the, un sab men sarpa dhoorta tha, aur us ne sree se kaha, kya sach haai, ki parameshvar ne kaha, ki tum is battkai ke kisee vraksha ka fal n khana ?
unhon ne us se kaha, ham dono ne svapn dekha haai, aur unake fal ka batanevala koi bhee naheen. yoosufa ne un se kaha, kya svapnon ka fal kahana parameshvar ka kam naheen haai? mujhe apana apana svapn batao.
yoosufa ne firaun se kaha, maai to kuchh naheen janata : parameshvar hee firaun ke liye shuubh vachan dega.
sukal ke saton vasharen men boomi bahutayat se ann upajatee rahee.
unhon ne apas men kaha, nisndeh ham apane bhai ke vishay men doshaee haai, kyonki jab us ne ham se gidgidake binatee kee, taubhee ham ne yah dekhkar, ki usaka jeevan kese sankatt men pada haai, usakee n sunee isee karan ham bhee ab is sankatt men pade haain.
aur sarvashaaktaiman ishvar us puroosh ko tum par dayalu karega, jis se ki vah tumhare doosare bhai ko aur binyameen ko bhee ane de : aur yaadi maain nirvansh hua to hone do.
is par ve faurtee se apane apane bore ko utar boomi par rakhkar unhen kholane lage.
is reeati ab mujh ko yahan par bhejanevale tum nahee, parameshvar hee tthara: aur usee ne mujhe firaun ka pita sa, aur usake sare ghar ka svamee, aur sare misr desh ka prabhu tthara diya haai.
aur levee ke putra, gesharen, kahat, aur mararee the.
tab firaun ne yakoob se poochha, teree avastha kitane din kee hui haai?
tab israael ko yoosufa ke putra dekh pade, aur us ne poochha, ye kaun haain ?
dan marga men ka aek sanp, aur raste men ka aek nag hoga, jo ghaede kee nalee ko dnsata haai, ajis se usaka savar pachhad khakar gir padta haai..
is karan yahova ne us se kaha, jo koi kaain ko ghaat karega us se sat guna palatta liya jaaega. aur yahova ne kaain ke liye aek chinh ttharaya aeesa ne ho ki koi use pakar mar dale..
yadhypi tum logon ne mere liye burai ka vichar kiya tha parantu parameshvar ne usee bat men bhlai ka vichar kiya, jis se vah aeesa kare, jaaisa aj ke din pragatt haai, ki bahut se logon ke praan bache haain.
jab matoosholah aek sau sattasee varsha ka hua, tab us ne lemek ko janm diya.
sab jaati ke shuuddh pashuuon men se to too sat sat, arthata nar aur mada lena : par jo pashu shuuddh naheen haai, un men se do do lena, arthata nar aur mada :
us kabootaree ko apane paair ke tale ttekane ke liye koi adhaar ne mila, so vah usake pas jahaj men lautt ai : kyonki saree prathvee ke upar jal hee jal chhaya tha tab us ne hath baddhakar use apane pas jahaja men le liya.
nooh ke jo putra jahaja men se nikale, ve shom, ham, aur yepet the : aur ham to kanan ka pita hua.
taubhee yahova ne firaun ke man ko kattor kar diya, jis se us ne israaeliyon ko jane n diya.
kyonaki us rat ko maain misr desh ke beech men se hokar jaunga, aur misr desh ke kya manushy kya pashu, sab ke pahilautton ko maroonga aur misr ke sare devataon ko bhee maain dand doonga maain to yahova hoon.
fir yahova ne moosa aur haroon se kaha, pabrba kee vidhai yah haai ki koi paradeshaee us men se n khaae
yahova ne moosa se kaha,
tab moosa aur israaeliyon ne yahova ke liye yah geet gaya. unhon ne kaha, maain yahova ka geet gaunga, kyonaki vah mahapratapee tthara haai ghaedon samet savaron ko us ne samudr men dal diya haai..
aur aeesa hoga ki chhttven din vah bhojan aur dinon se doona hoga, isaaliye jo kuchh ve us din battoren use taaiyar kar rakhen.
aek omer to aepa ka dasavan bhag haai.
moosa ne apane sasur se kaha, isaka karan yah haai ki log mere pas parameshvar se poochhne ate haai.
aur yahova seenaai parvat kee chottee par utara aur moosa ko parvat kee chottee par bulaya aur moosa upar chaddh gaya.
too apane liye koi moorti khodakar n banana, n kisee ki pratima banana, jo akash me, va prathvee par, va prathvee ke jal men haai.
aur yaadi us ne use apane bette ko byah diya ho, to us se bettee ka sa vyavahar kare.
yaadi churaya hua baail, va gadaha, va bhed va bakaree usake hath men jeevit pai jaa, to vah usaka doona bhr de..
yaadi tere shatra ka baail va gadaha bhttkata hua tujhe mile, to use usake pas avashy faer le ana.
aur keval moosa yahova ke sameep aae parantu ve sameep n aae, aur doosare log usake sang upar n aaen.
ve dnde sandook ke kadon men lage rahen aur us se alag n kiae jaaen.
aur sone ke pachas ankade banavana aur paradon ke pancho ko ankadon ke dara aek doosare se aeesa judvana ki nivasasthan milakar aek hee ho jaae.
aur is parde ke liye babool ke panch khmbhe banavana, aur unako sone se maddhvana unakee kadyaian sone kee ho, aur unake liye peetal kee panch kuarsiyan ddhlava kar banavana..
unake namon men se chh: to ek manai par, aur shosh chh: nam doosare maanai par, israel ke putraen kee utpati ke anusar khudavana.
apane bhai haroon aur usake putraen ko ye hee sab vasr pahinakar unaka abhaishok aur sanskar karana, aur unhen pavitra karana, ki ve mere liye yajak ka kam karen.
aur haroon ke jo pavitra vasr honge vah usake bad usake bette pote adi ko milate rahe, jis se unheen ko pahine huae unaka abhaishok aur sanskar kiya jaae.
us ne kaha, kis ne tujhe ham logon par hakim aur nyayee ttharaya ? jis bhanati too ne misree ko ghaat kiya kya usee bhanti too mujhe bhee ghaat karana chahata haai ? tab moosa yah sochakar dr gaya, ki nishchay vah bat khul gai haai.
jab jab ve milapavale tamboo men pravesh karen tab tab ve hath panv jal se dhaeae, naheen to mar jaaenge aur jab jab ve vedee ke pas seva tthal karane, arthata yahova ke liye havy jalane ko aaen tab tab ve hath panv dhaeae, n ho ki mar jaaen.
too israaeliyon se yah bhee kahana, ki nishchay tum mere vishraamadinon ko manana, kyonaki tumharee peeddhee peeddhee men mere aur tum logon ke beech yah aek chinh tthara haai, jis se tum yah bat jan rakho ki yahova hamara pavitra karanehara haai.
unako nirankush dekhkar moosa ne chhavanee ke nikas par khde hokar kaha, jo koi yahova kee or ka ho vah mere pas ae tab sare leveey us ke pas ikatthe hue.
aur jab tak mera tej tere samhane hoke chalata rahe tab tak maai tujhe chattan ke darar men rakoonga, aur jab tak maain tere samhane hokar n nikal jaun tab tak apane hath se tujhe ddhanpe rahoonga
jab haroon aur sab israaeliyon ne moosa ko dekha ki usake chehare se kiranen nikalatee haai, tab ve usake pas jane se dr gaae.
aur jitanee striayon ke man men aeesee buaddh ika prakash tha unho ne bakaree ke bal bhee kate.
aek aek takhte men aek doosaree se jodee hui do do choolen banee, nivas ke sab takhton ke liyen us ne isee bhnaati banain.
aur us ne menja uttane ke liye dndon ko babool kee lakadee ke banaya, aur sone se maddha.
aur khmbhon kee kuarsiyan peetal kee, aur ghaundyaian aur chhde chandee kee banee, aur unake sire chandee se maddhe gaa, aur angan ke sab khmbhe chandee ke chhdon se jode gaae the.
tab unhon ne sone kee donon goonthee hui janjeero ko chaparas ke siron par kee donon kadiyon men lagaya.
us ne kaha idhar pas mat a, aur apane panvon se jootiyon ko utar de, kyonki jis sthan par too khda haai vah paavitra boomi haai.
aur usake putraen ko le jakar angarakhe pahinana,
tab us ne kaha, apana hath chhatee par fir rakhkar ddhanpa. aur us ne apana hath chhatee par rakhkar ddhanp liya aur jab us ne usako chhatee par se nikala tab kya dekhta haai, ki vah fir saree deh ke saman ho gaya.
ki tum jo ab tak itten banane ke liye logon ko pual diya karate the so age ko n dena ve ap hee jakar apane liye pual ikattha karen.
aur shaimon ke putra : yamooael, yameen, ohad, yaakin, aur sohar the, aur aek kananee sree ka betta shaaul bhee tha inheen se shaimon ke kul nikale.
aur us se is prakar kahana, ki ibiryon ke parameshvar yahova ne mujhe yah kahane ke liye tere pas bheja haai, ki meree praja ke logon ko jane de ki jis se ve jangal men meree upasana karen aur ab tak too ne mera kahana naheen mana.
aur maain apanee praja aur teree praja men antar ttharaunga. yah chinh kal hoga.
tak yahova ne moosa se kaha, apana hath akash kee or baddha, ki sare misr desh ke manushyon pashuuon aur kheton kee saree upaj par ole giren.
dekho, usaka lohoo paavitrasthan ke bheetar to laya hee naheen gaya, ni:sandeh uchit tha ki tum meree agyaa ke anusar usake mans ko paavitrasthan men khate.
aur jo prathvee par rengate haain un men se ye renganevale tumhare liye ashuuddh haai, arthata nevala, chooha, aur bhanati bhanati ke goh,
aur sataven din yajak usako dekhe, aur yadi vah vyaadhai jaaisee kee taaisee banee rahe aur usake charma men n faailee ho, to yajak usako aur bhee sat din tak bandakar rakhe
to yajak usako dekhe, aur yaadi vah charma men faaila ho, to yajak yah boore bal n ddoonddhe, kyonaki manushy ashuuddh haai.
