aur sataven din yajak akar dekhe aur yaadi vah vyaadhai ghar kee deevaron par faail gai ho,
fir jisake prameh ho vah jab apane rog se changa ho jaa, tab se shuuddh ttharane ke sat din gin le, aur unake beetane par apane vasren ko dhaekar bahate huae jal se snan kare tab vah shuuddh ttharega.
aur haroon us papabali ke bachhde ko jo usee ke liye hoga sameep le aa, aur usako balidan karake apane aur apane gharane ke liye praayaashchaitt kare.
