aur chauthe varsha men unake sab fal yahova kee stuti karane ke liye paavitra ttharen.
fir yahova ne moosa se kaha,
ve n to apane sir mundaae, aur n apane gal ke balon ko mundaae, aur n apane shareer cheeren.
