parantu apanee saree vastuon men se jo kuchh koi yahova ke liye arpan kare, chahe manushy ho chahe pashu, chahe usakee nij boomi ka khet ho, aeesee koi arpan kee hui vastu n to bechee jaae aur n chhudai jaae jo kuchh arpan kiya jaae vah yahova ke liye paramapavitra tthare.
