aur raja ne saree praja ke logon ko agyaa dee, ki is vacha kee pustak men jo kuchh likha haai, usake anusar apane parameshvar yahova ke liye fasah ka parva mano.
aur vah yahoyakeen ko babel men le gaya aur usakee mata aur striayon aur khojon ko aur desh ke bade logon ko vah bandhaua karake yarooshalem se babel ko le gaya.
fir yahooda ke raja yahoyakeen kee bandhauai ke taainteesaven varsha men arthata jis varsha men babel ka raja aeveelmarodak rajagaee par virajaman hua, usee ke barahaven maheene ke sattaisaven din ko us ne yahooda ke raja yahoyakeen ko bandeegrah se nikalakar bada pad diya.
taubhee vah nabat ke putra yarobam ke aeese papon men jaaise us ne israaael se bhee karaae lipatta raha aur un se n fira.
tab us ne jakar parameshvar ke bhkt ko yah bata diya. or us ne kaha, ja tel bechakar ren bhr de aur jo rah jaa, us se too apane putraen sahit apana nirvah karana.
tab aeleesha gilagal ko lautt gaya. us samay desh men akal tha, aur bhvishyadvktaon ke chele usake samhane baaitte huae the, aur us ne apane sevak se kaha, handa chaddhakar bhvishyadvktaon ke chelon ke liye kuchh paka.
aur vah bheetar jakar, apane svamee ke samhane khda hua. aeleesha ne us se poochha, he gehajee too kahan se ata haai? us ne kaha, tera das to kaheen naheen gaya,
tab mere bette ko pakakar ham ne kha liya, fir doosare din jab maain ne is se kaha ki apana betta de ki ham use kha le, tab is ne apane bette ko chhpai rakha.
aur aeleesha daamishak ko gaya. aur jab aram ke raja benhadad ko jo rogee tha yah samachar mila, ki parameshvar ka bhkt yahan bhee aya haai,
aur maain ahab ka gharana nabat ke putra yarobam ka sa, aur aahiyyah ke putra basha ka sa kar doonga.
kyonaki usake ishvareey samarth ne sab kuchh jo jeevan aur bhktai se sambandha rakhta haai, hamen usee kee pahachan ke dara diya haai, jis ne hamen apanee hee maahima aur sadagun ke anusar bulaya haai.
auron ka bura karane ke badale unheen ka bura hoga: unhen din dopahar sukh-vilas karana bhla lagata haai yah kalank aur dosh haai- jab ve tumhare sath khate peete haai, to apanee or se praem bhoj karake bhoga-avilas karate haain.
isaliye hanoon ne daud ke karmachariyon ko pakada, aur unakee adhaee-adhaee daddhee mudvakar aur adho vasr, arthata nitamb tak kattvakar, unako jane diya.
aur yoab ne nagar ko achchhee reeati se dekh bhalakar jis sthan men vah janata tha ki veer haai, usee men uriyyah ko tthara diya.
tab daud boomi par se utta, aur nahakar tel lagaya, aur vasr badala tab yahova ke bhvan men jakar dandvata kee fir apane bhvan men aya aur usakee agyaa par rottee usako parosee gai, aur us ne bhojan kiya.
usake bhai abashaalom ne us se poochha, kya tera bhai amnon tere sath raha haai? parantu ab, he meree baahin, chup rah, vah to tera bhai haai is bat kee chinta n kara. tab tamar apane bhai abashaalom ke ghar men man mare baaittee rahee.
sree bolee, teree dasee apane prabhu raja se aek bat kahane paae.
tab abashaalom ne israaael ke samast gotron men yah kahane ke liye bheadiae bheje, ki jag naraasinge ka shabd tum ko sun pade, tab kahana, ki abashaalom hebraen men raja hua !
raja ne seeba se kaha, jo kuchh mapeeboshot ka tha vah sab tujhe mil gaya. seeba ne kaha, pranama he mere prabhu, he raja, mujh par tere anugrah kee draashtti banee rahe.
aur jab ham usako kisee n kisee sthan men jahan vah mile ja pakadenge, tab jaaise os boomi par giratee haai vaaise hee ham us par toott padenge tab n to vah bachega, aur n usake sangiyon men se koi bachega.
yoab ne kaha, maain tere sang yonhee tthara naheen rah sakata ! so us ne teen lakadee hath men lekar abashaalom ke day me, jo banj vraksha men jeevaati lattka tha, chhed dala.
tum log to mere bhai, varan meree hee haddee aur mans ho to tum raja ko lauttane men sab ke peechhe kyon hote ho?
israaaelee purushaen ne yahoodee purushaen ko uttar diya, raja men das ansh hamare haain aur daud men hamara bhag tumhare bhag se bada haai. to fir tum ne hamen kyon tuchchh jana? kya apane raja ke lautta le ane kee charcha paahile ham hee ne n kee thee? aur yahoodee purushaen ne israaaelee purushaen se aadhaik kadee baten kaheen.
tab raja ne amasa se kaha, yahoodee purushaen ko teen din ke bheetar mere pas bula la, aur too bhee yahan upaasthiat rahana.
giboniyon ke hath saunp diya, aur unhon ne unhen pahad par yahova ke samhane faansee dee, aur saton aek sath nash hue. unaka mar dala jana to kattnee ke pahile dinon me, arthata jab kee kattnee ke arambh men hua.
us ne mujhe mere balavant shatra se, aur mere baaiariyon se, jo mujh se aadhaik samath the, mujhe chhuda liya.
aur mujhe mere shatrauon ke beech se nikalata haai ha, too mujhe mere virodhaiyon se uncha karata haai, aur upadravee purush se bachata haai.
aek aur natopahee bana ka putra heleb, binyameeaniyon ke giba nagar ke reebaai ka putra huttaai,
aur arauna ne kaha, mera prabhu raja apane das ke pas kyon padhaara haai? aud ne kaha, tujh se yah khlihan mol lene aya hoo, ki yahova kee aek bedee banavau, isaaliye ki yah vyaadhai praja par se door kee jaae.
yoab ne kaha, parameshvar ke jeevan kee shapat, ki yadi too n bola hota, to nisandeh log savere hee chale jate, aur apane apane bhai ka peechha n karate.
yoab ne daud ke pas se nikalakar daud ke anajane abner ke peechhe doot bheje, aur ve usako seera nam kund se lautta le aae.
taubhee daud ne siyyon nam gaddh ko le liya, vahee daudapur bhee kahalata haai.
jab yahova ke sandook ke uttanevale chh kadam chal chuke, tab daud ne aek baail aur aek pala posa hua bachhda bali karaya.
too ne apane vachan ke nimit, aur apane hee man ke anusar, yah sab bada kam kiya haai, ki tera das usako jan le.
tab raja daud ne doot bhejakar usako lodabar se, ammeeael ke putra makeer ke ghar se bulava liya.
aur isee karan parameshvar un men aek bhttka denevalee samarth ko bhejega taki ve joott kee prateeti karen.
kyonaki parameshvar ne hamen bhy kee naheen par samarth, aur praem, aur sanyam kee atma dee haai.
bade ghar men n keval sone-chandee hee ke, par katt aur mittee ke baratan bhee hote haain koi koi adar, aur koi koi anadar ke liye.
bhavishy men mere liye dharma ka vah mukutt rakha hua haai, jise prabhu, jo dharmee, aur nyayee haai, mujhe us din dega aur mujhe hee nahee, baran un sab ko bhee, jo usake pragatt hone ko piry janate haain..
isaliye maain moab men ag lagaunga, aur us se kaariyyot ke bhvan bhsm ho jaaenge aur moab hullad aur lalakar, aur narasinge ke shabd hote-hote mar jaaega.
parameshvar yahova apanee paavitrata kee shapath khakar kahata haai, dekho, tum par aeese din anevale haai, ki tum kattyaiaon se, aur tumharee santan machhlee kee baansaiyon se kheench liae jaaenge.
kya yah sach naheen haai ki yahova ka din ujiyale ka nahee, varan aandhiayare hee ka hoga? ha, aeese ghaer andhakar ka jis men kuchh bhee chamak n ho..
tab betel ke yajak amasyah ne israael ke raja yarobam ke pas kahala bheja, ki, amos ne israael ke gharane ke beech men tujh se rajadraeh kee goshttee kee haai usake sare vachanon ko desh naheen sah sakata.
meree praja men ke sab papee jo kahate haain ki vah vipaati ham par n padegee, aur n hamen ghoregee, ve sab talavar se mare jaaenge.
tab mallah log drakar apane apane devata kee dohai dene lage aur jahaj men jo vyopar kee samagraee thee use samudra men faenkane lage ki jahaj halka ho jaae. parantu yona jahaj ke nichale bhag men utarakar so gaya tha, aur gaharee neend men pada hua tha.
sambhv haai, parameshvar daya kare aur apanee ichchha badal de, aur usaka bhdka hua kop shaant ho jaae aur ham nash hone se bach jaaen..
is kara, yahova yon kahata haai, maain is kul par aeesee vipaati dalane par hoo, jis ke neeche se tum apanee gardan hatta n sakoge kyonki vah vipaati ka samay hoga.
ab too kyon chillatee haai? kya tujh men koi raja naheen raha? kya tera yuaktai karanevala nash ho gaya, jis se jachcha sree kee nain tujhe peeda utttee haai?
yahan ke dhanavana log upadrav ka kam dekha karate haain aur yahan ke sab rahanevale joott bolate haain aur unake munh se chhl kee baten nikalatee haain.
yahova bhla haai sankatt ke din men vah draddh gaddh ttharata haai, aur apane sharanagaton kee sudhaee rakhta haai.
taubhee usako bandhauvai men le gaa, aur usake nanhen bachche sadkon ke sire par pattk diae gaae aur usake praatishttit purooshaen ke liye unhon ne chitthee dalee, aur usake sab rais beadiyon se jakade gaae.
dakhmadha se dhaekha hota haai ahankaree puroosh ghar men naheen rahata, aur usakee lalasa adhaelok ke saman pooree naheen hotee, aur mratyu kee nain usaka pett naheen bhrata. vah sab jaatiyon ko apane pas kheench leta, aur sab deshaen ke logon ko apane pas ikatthe kar rakhta haai..
yah sab sunate hee mera kaleja kanp utta, mere ontt thrathrane lage meree haddiyan sadne lagee, aur maain khde khde kanpane laga. maain shaaantai se us din kee batt johata rahoonga jab dal bandhakar praja chaddhai kare..
yah unake garva ka palatta hoga, kyonaki unhon ne senaon ke yahova kee praja kee namadharai kee, aur us par badai maree haai.
tum ne bahut boya parantu thoda katta tum khate ho, parantu pett naheen bhrata tum peete ho, parantu pyas naheen bujhtee tum kapade paahinate ho, parantu garamate naheen aur jo majadooree kamata haai, vah apanee majadooree kee kamai ko chhedavalee thailee men rakhta haai..
aur maain rajya-rajy kee gaee ko ulatt doonga maain anyajatiyon ke rajya-rajy ka bal tooonga, aur rathon ko chaddhvaaiyon samet ulatt doonga aur ghaedon samet savar aek doosare kee talavar se girenge.
israael ke vishay men yahova ka kaha hua bharee vachana: yahova ko akash ka tananevala, prathvee kee nev dalanevala aur manushy kee atma ka rachanevala haai, usakee yah vanee haai,
tab yahova saree prathvee ka raja hoga aur us samay aek hee yahova aur usaka nam bhee aek hee mana jaaega..
tab jo doot mujh se baten karata tha, us se maain ne poochha, ye kya haain? us ne mujh se kaha, ye ve hee seeng haai, jinhon ne yahooda aur israael aur yarooshalem ko titara-abitar kiya haai.
tab us ne mujhe uttr dekar kaha, jaroobbabel ke liye yahova ka yah vachan haai: n to bal se, aur n shaaktai se, parantu mere atma ke dara hoga, mujh senaon ke yahova ka yahee vachan haai.
vahee yahova ke mandair ko banaaega, aur mahima paaega, aur apane sinhasan par virajaman hokar prabhuta karega. aur usake sinhasan ke pas aek yajak bhee rahega, aur donon ke beech mel kee sammaati hogee.
usee prakar maain ne in dinon men yarooshalem kee aur yahooda ke gharane kee bhlai karane ko ttana haai isaliye tum mat dro.
putra pita ka, aur das svamee ka adar karata haai. yaadi maain pita hoo, to mera adar manana kahan haai? aur yadi maain svamee hoo, to mera bhy manana kahan? senaon ka yahova, tum yajakon se bhee jo mere nam ka apaman karate ho yahee bat poochhta haai. parantu tum poochhte ho, ham ne kis bat men tere nam ka apaman kiya haai? tum meree vedee par ashuuddh bhojan chaddhate ho.
kyonaki maain yahova badalata naheen isee kara, he yakoob kee santan tum nash naheen hue.
mujhe tujh ko bahut kuchh likhna to tha par siyahee aur kalam se likhna naheen chahata.
tumhare sir ke bal bhee sab gine huae haain.
manushy ka putra khata-peeta aya, aur ve kahate haain ki dekho, petoo aur piyakkad manushy, mahasool lenevalon aur paapiyon ka mitra par gyaan apane kamon men sachcha ttharaya gaya haai.
vah kuchale huae sarakande ko n todega aur dhooan detee hui battee ko n bujhaaega, jab tak nyay ko prabal n karaae.
usee din yeeshu ghar se nikalakar jheel ke kinare ja baaitta.
vah sab beejon se chhotta to haai par jab baddh jata haai tab sab sag pat se bada hota haai aur aeesa ped ho jata haai, ki akash ke pakshaee akar us kee daliyon par basera karate haain..
aur vah use mar dalana chahata tha, par logon se drata tha, kyonaki ve use bhavishyadvkta janate the.
aur us se binatee karane lage, ki vah unhen apane vasr ke anchal hee ko choone de: aur jitanaen ne use chooa, ve change ho gaae..
so jab logon ne dekha, ki goonge bolate aur ttunde change hote aur langade chalate aur andho dekhte haai, to achambha karake israael ke parameshvar kee badai kee..
us ne firakar pataras se kaha, he shautan, mere samhane se door ho: too mere liye ttokar ka karan haai kyonki too parameshvar kee baten nahee, par manushyon kee baton par man lagata haai.
yeeshu n us se kaha, to putra bach gaae.
us ne n mana, parantu jakar use bandeegrah men dal diya ki jab tak karja ko bhr n de, tab tak vaheen rahe.
yeeshu ne un kee or dekhkar kaha, manushyon se to yah naheen ho sakata, parantu parameshvar se sab kuchh ho sakata haai.
aur us ne majadooron se aek deenar raj par ttharakar, unhen apane dakh kee baree men bheja.
tum kya chahate ho ki maain tumhare liye karoon? unhon ne us se kaha, he prabhu yah ki hamaree ankhe khul jaaen.
fir doosare ke pas jakar aeesa hee kaha, us ne uttr diya, jee han jata hoo, parantu naheen gaya.
tab fareesiyon ne jakar apas men vichar kiya, ki us ko kis prakar baton men fansaaen.
usake uttr men koi bhee ek bat n kah saka parantu us din se kisee ko fir us se kuchh poochhne ka hiyav n hua..
so tum apane bapadadon ke pap ka ghada bhr do.
kyonaki jootte maseeh aur jootte bhavishyadvkta utt khde honge, aur bade chinh aur adabhut kam dikhaaenge, ki yadi ho sake to chune huon ko bhee bhrama den.
parantu samajhdaron ne apanee mashaalon ke sath apanee kuappaiyon men tel bhee bhr liya.
kayonaki maai. bookha tha, aur tum ne mujhe khane ko diya maain piyasa tha, aur tum ne mujhe panee pilaya, maain paradeshaee tha, tum ne mujhe apane ghar men ttharaya.
jab sanjh hui, to vah barahon ke sath bhojan karane ke liye baaitta.
aur dekho, yeeshu ke saathaiyon men se aek ne hath baddhakar apanee talavar kheench lee aur mahayajak ke das par chalakar us ka kan uda diya.
so unhon ne sammaati karake un sikkon se paradeshaiyon ke gadne ke liye kumhar ka khet mol le liya.
aur ane jane vale sir hila hilakar us kee ninda karate the.
usake bhy se paharooae kanp utte, aur mratak saman ho gae.
aur herodes ke marane tak vaheen raha isaliye ki vah vachan jo prabhu ne bhvishyadvkta ke dara kaha tha ki maain ne apane putra ko misr se bulaya poora ho.
aur us se kaha yadi too parameshvar ka putra haai, to apane ap ko neeche gira de kyonaki likha haai, ki vah tere vishay men apane svargadooton ko agyaa dega aur ve tujhe hathon hath utta lenge kaheen aeesa n ho ki tere panvon men patthr se ttes lage.
tum prathvee ke namak ho parantu yaadi namak ka svad bigad jaa, to vah fir kis vastu se namakeen kiya jaaega?
tum sun chuke ho, ki kaha gaya tha ki apane padosee se praem rakhna, aur apane baairee se baaira.
akash ke paakshiayon ko dekho! ve n bote haai, n kattte haai, aur n khton men battorate haain taubhee tumhara svargeey pita un ko khailata haai kya tum un se adhaik mooly naheen rakhte.
tab maain un se khulakar kah doonga ki maain ne tum ko kabhee naheen jana, he kukarma karanevalo, mere pas se chale jao.
tab unhon ne pas akar use jagaya, aur kaha, he prabhu, hamen bacha, ham nash huae jate haain.
yeeshu ne firakar use dekha, aur kaha putraee ddhaddhs bandha tere vishvas ne tujhe changa kiya haai so vah sree usee ghadee changee ho gai.
maain tum se sach kahata hoo, ki jo koi parameshvar ke rajy ko balak kee nai grahan n kare, vah us men kabhee pravesh karane n paaega.
aur ve yareeho men aa, aur jab vah aur usake chele, aur aek badee bheed yareeho se nikalatee thee, to timai ka putra baratimai aek andha bhaikharee sadk ke kinare baaitta tha.
aur jab kabhee tum khde huae praarthna karate ho, to yadi tumhare man men kisee kee aur se kuchh virodha, ho to kshama karo: isaaliye ki tumhara svargeey pita bhee tumhare aparadha kshama kare..
so jee uttne par vah un men se kis kee patnee hogee? kyonaki vah saton kee patnee ho chukee thee.
par avashy haai ki pahile susamachar sab jatiyon men prachar kiya jaae.
parantu koi koi apane man men risiyakar kahane lage, is itra ko kyon satyanash kiya gaya?
aur vah thoda age baddha, aur boomi par girakar praarthna karane laga, ki yadi ho sake to yah ghadee mujh par se ttl jaae.
jab pataras neeche angan men tha, to mahayajak kee laundyaien men se aek vahan ai.
aur pahar din chaddha tha, jab unhon ne us ko kroos par chaddhaya.
saptah ke paahile din bhor hote hee vah jee utt kar paahile paahil mariyam magadaleenee ko jis men se us ne sat dushttatmaaen nikalee thee, dikhai diya.
us ne turant unhen bulaya aur ve apane pita jabadee ko majadooree ke sath nav par chhodkar, usake peechhe chale gae..
tab kai aek shaasree jo vahan baaitte the, apane apane man men vichar karane lage.
aur us ne apane chelon se kaha, bheed ke karan aek chhottee nav mere liye taaiyar rahe taki ve mujhe daba n saken.
aur kuchh patthreelee boomi par gira jahan us kee bahut mittee n milee, aur gaharee mittee n milane ke karan jald ug aya.
aur ve bheed ko chhodkar jaaisa vah tha, vaaisa kee use nav par sath le chale aur usake sat, aur bhee naven theen.
aur jis ne bahut vaaidhon se bada dukh uttaya aur apana sab mal vyay karane par bhee kuchh labh n uttaya tha, parantu aur bhee rogee ho gai thee.
aur herodes raja ne us kee charcha sunee, kyonki usaka nam faail gaya tha, aur us ne kaha, ki yoohanna bapatisma denevala mare huon men se jee utta haai, isee liye us se ye samarth ke kam pragatt hote haain.
tab us ne turant apane chelon ko barabas nav par chaddhaya, ki ve us se pahile us par baaitasaaida ko chale jana, jab tak ki vah logon ko vida kare.
fir us ne kaha jo manushy men se nikalata haai, vahee manushy ko ashuuddh karata haai.
aur us ne unhen chitaya, ki dekho, fareesiyon ke khmeer aur herodes ke khmeer se chaukas raho.
tab unhon ne aekaaek charon aur draashtti kee, aur yeeshu ko chhod apane sath aur kisee ko n dekha..
yeeshu ne kaha, us ko mat mana karo kyonaki aeesa koi naheen jo mere nam se samarth ka kam kare, aur jaldee se mujhe bura kah sake.
usee ghadee vah pavitra atma men hokar anand se bhr gaya, aur kaha he pita, svarga aur prathvee ke prabhu, maain tera dhanyavad karata hoo, ki too ne in baton ko gyaaaniyon aur samajhdaron se chhpai rakha, aur balakon par pragatt kiya: ha, he pit, kyonaki tujhe yahee achchha laga.
kyonaki jo koi mangata haai, use milata haai aur jo ddoonddhta haai, vah pata haai aur jo khttkhttata haai, usake liye khola jaaega.
parantu ha, bheetaravalee vastuon ko dan kar do, to dekho, sab kuchh tumhare liye shuuddh ho jaaega..
aur us ne kaha maain yah karoonga: maain apanee bakhariyan tod kar un se badee banaunga
maain prathvee par ag lagane aya hoon aur kya chahata hoon keval yah ki abhee sulag jatee !
vah khmeer ke saman haai, jis ko kisee sree ne lekar teen paseree atte men milaya, aur hote hote sab atta khmeer ho gaya..
jab bhojan taaiyar ho gaya, to us ne apane das ke hath nevatahariyon ko kahala bheja, ki ao ab bhojan taaiyar haai.
aur bahut din n beete the ki chhuttka putra sab kuchh ikattha karake aek door desh ko chala gaya aur vahan kukarma men apanee sanpati uda dee.
aur yaadi tum paraye dhan men sachche n tthare, to jo tumhara haai, use tumhen kaun dega?
aur kisee ganv men pravesh karate samay use das koddhee mile.
prabhu ne kaha, suno, ki yah adharmee nyayee kya kahata haai?
unhon ne us ko bataya, ki yeeshu nasaree ja raha haai.
unhon ne us se kaha he svamee, usake pas das moharen to haain.
jab vah apane dalakee paree par parameshvar ke samhane yajak ka kam karata tha.
un dinon men maariyam uttkar shaeegha hee pahadee desh men yahooda ke ek nagar ko gai.
jaaise us ne apane paavitra bhavishyadvktaon ke dara jo jagat ke adi se hote aae haai, kaha tha.
unhon ne us se yah poochha, ki he guro, ham janate haain ki too tteek kahata, aur sikhata bhee haai, aur kisee ka pakshapat naheen karata baran parameshvar ka marga sachchai se batata haai.
jab kitane log mandair ke vishay men kah rahe the, ki vah kaaise sundar patthron aur bhentt kee vastuon se sanvara gaya haai to us ne kaha.
isaliye jagate raho aur har samay praarthna karate raho ki tum in sab anevalee ghattnaon se bachane, aur manushy ke putra ke samhane khde hone ke yogy bano..
aur jaaise mere pita ne mere liye aek rajy ttharaya haai,
pataras ne kaha, he manushy, maain naheen janata ki too kya kahata haai? vah kah hee raha tha ki turant murga ne bang dee.
parantu unhon ne chillakar kaha: ki use kroos par chaddha, kroos para.
us ne peelatus ke pas jakar yeeshu kee loth mang lee.
tab us ne moosa se aur sab bhavishyadvktaon se arambh karake sare paavitra shaasren men se, apane vishay men kee baton ka arth, unhen samajha diya.
ki apanee mangetar maariyam ke sath jo garbhvatee thee nam likhvaae.
aur ashor ke gotra men se hannah nam fanooael kee bettee aek bhavishyadvaktain thee: vah bahut booddhee thee, aur byah hone ke bad sat varsha apane paati ke sath rah pai thee.
